  <amendments/>
  <summary>1/6/1987--Introduced.
Provides a limited antitrust exemption from State and Federal laws for: (1) actions taken to develop independent natural gas producers' cooperative associations; or (2) actions taken by such associations to implement plans to market natural gas in interstate commerce. Conditions such exemption upon such actions': (1) being necessary to market natural gas; and (2) not being taken for the purpose of reducing competition.</summary>
